casebody.head_matter:
In Re Jaron R. BRICE, petitioner.
No. 17-8584.
Supreme Court of the United States
May 14, 2018.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis is denied, and petition for a writ of habeas corpus dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
